description:
EnmityYou

Allows you to access Enmity's settings on the experimental new YouTab which was introduced several versions ago but is now force-enabled by Discord in the new alphas with the Tabs UI enabled. Previews for this plugin are provided below.

(*Notes:*
*- You may need to disable the new Tabs UI to install the plugin, after which point you should be able to enable it again.*
*- If you experience any crashes when attempting to open the new YouTab, please restart your client and try again.*
*- If you're on an older alpha, aka any Discord version under 180, please do* *not* *use this. It will not work.*)

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/acquitelol/enmity-you/mistress/dist/EnmityYou.js
Source: https://github.com/acquitelol/enmity-you
